{"_id":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","slug":"kind-words","name":"Kind Words","verses":[{"_id":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c5","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 16:24","votes":136,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20016024_01-1\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20016024-1\">24&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Gracious words are like a honeycomb,</span><br><span id=\"p20016024_01-1\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sweetness to the soul and health to the body.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","kjv":"<strong>24</strong> Pleasant words are as an honeycomb, sweet to the soul, and health to the bones.  ","modified":"2023-07-01T14:53:50.547Z"},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04c6","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"1 Thessalonians 5:11","votes":61,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p52005011_01-3\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v52005011-1\">11&nbsp;</b>Therefore encourage one another and build one another up, just as you are doing.</p>\n</div>","modified":"2023-04-12T11:24:31.044Z"},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04c8","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Ephesians 4:29","votes":95,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p49004029_01-4\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v49004029-1\">29&nbsp;</b>Let no corrupting talk come out of your mouths, but only such as is good for building up, as fits the occasion, that it may give grace to those who hear.</p>\n</div>","modified":"2023-08-18T00:19:11.918Z"},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04c7","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 15:1","votes":102,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20015001_01-5\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"chapter-num\" id=\"v20015001-1\">15:1&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;A soft answer turns away wrath,</span><br><span id=\"p20015001_01-5\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;but a harsh word stirs up anger.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","modified":"2023-07-01T14:53:53.756Z"},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04c9","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Colossians 4:6","votes":57,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p51004006_01-6\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v51004006-1\">6&nbsp;</b>Let your speech always be gracious, seasoned with salt, so that you may know how you ought to answer each person.</p>\n</div>","modified":"2023-04-12T11:24:23.929Z"},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04ca","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Job 4:4","votes":51,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p18004004_01-7\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v18004004-1\">4&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Your words have upheld him who was stumbling,</span><br><span id=\"p18004004_01-7\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and you have made firm the feeble knees.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","kjv":"<strong>4</strong> Thy words have upholden him that was falling, and thou hast strengthened the feeble knees.  "},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04cb","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 25:11","votes":45,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20025011_01-8\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20025011-1\">11&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;A word fitly spoken</span><br><span id=\"p20025011_01-8\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;is like apples of gold in a setting of silver.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","kjv":"<strong>11</strong> A word fitly spoken is like apples of gold in pictures of silver.  "},{"_id":"6164f3136451fe5325fa04cc","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 15:23","votes":37,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20015023_01-9\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20015023-1\">23&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;To make an apt answer is a joy to a man,</span><br><span id=\"p20015023_01-9\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and a word in season, how good it is!</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","modified":"2023-08-17T21:19:08.470Z"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04cd","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Colossians 3:12","votes":24,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p51003012_01-10\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v51003012-1\">12&nbsp;</b>Put on then, as God’s chosen ones, holy and beloved, compassionate hearts, kindness, humility, meekness, and patience,</p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04cf","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Psalm 19:14","votes":33,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p19019014_01-11\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v19019014-1\">14&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Let the words of my mouth and the meditation of my heart</span><br><span id=\"p19019014_01-11\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;be acceptable in your sight,</span><br><span id=\"p19019014_01-11\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;O LORD, my rock and my redeemer.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","modified":"2023-01-24T14:33:03.579Z"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04ce","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 15:4","votes":20,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20015004_01-12\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20015004-1\">4&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;A gentle tongue is a tree of life,</span><br><span id=\"p20015004_01-12\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;but perverseness in it breaks the spirit.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04d0","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 12:18","votes":20,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20012018_01-13\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20012018-1\">18&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;There is one whose rash words are like sword thrusts,</span><br><span id=\"p20012018_01-13\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;but the tongue of the wise brings healing.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04d1","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Galatians 5:22-23","votes":17,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p48005022_01-14\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v48005022-1\">22&nbsp;</b>But the fruit of the Spirit is love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, faithfulness, <b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v48005023-1\">23&nbsp;</b>gentleness, self-control; against such things there is no law.</p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04d3","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"1 Corinthians 13:4","votes":19,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p46013004_01-16\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v46013004-1\">4&nbsp;</b>Love is patient and kind; love does not envy or boast; it is not arrogant</p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3156451fe5325fa04d2","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Ephesians 4:32","votes":18,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p49004032_01-17\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v49004032-1\">32&nbsp;</b>Be kind to one another, tenderhearted, forgiving one another, as God in Christ forgave you.</p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3166451fe5325fa04d4","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Matthew 12:36","votes":16,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p40012036_01-18\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num woc\" id=\"v40012036-1\">36&nbsp;</b><span class=\"woc\">I tell you, on the day of judgment people will give account for every careless word they speak,</span></p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3166451fe5325fa04d5","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"1 Peter 3:15","votes":15,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p60003015_01-20\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v60003015-1\">15&nbsp;</b>but in your hearts honor Christ the Lord as holy, always being prepared to make a defense to anyone who asks you for a reason for the hope that is in you; yet do it with gentleness and respect,</p>\n</div>","modified":"2023-04-11T06:00:04.263Z"},{"_id":"6164f3166451fe5325fa04d6","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 18:21","votes":17,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20018021_01-21\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20018021-1\">21&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Death and life are in the power of the tongue,</span><br><span id=\"p20018021_01-21\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and those who love it will eat its fruits.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3176451fe5325fa04d7","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Luke 6:35","votes":16,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p42006035_01-22\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num woc\" id=\"v42006035-1\">35&nbsp;</b><span class=\"woc\">But love your enemies, and do good, and lend, expecting nothing in return, and your reward will be great, and you will be sons of the Most High, for he is kind to the ungrateful and the evil.</span></p>\n</div>","modified":"2023-09-01T18:16:23.245Z"},{"_id":"6164f3176451fe5325fa04d8","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 12:25","votes":14,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20012025_01-23\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20012025-1\">25&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Anxiety in a man’s heart weighs him down,</span><br><span id=\"p20012025_01-23\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;but a good word makes him glad.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3176451fe5325fa04d9","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 31:26","votes":15,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20031026_01-24\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20031026-1\">26&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;She opens her mouth with wisdom,</span><br><span id=\"p20031026_01-24\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and the teaching of kindness is on her tongue.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3176451fe5325fa04da","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Galatians 5:22","votes":15,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p48005022_01-25\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v48005022-1\">22&nbsp;</b>But the fruit of the Spirit is love, joy, peace, patience, kindness, goodness, faithfulness,</p>\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3186451fe5325fa04db","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Acts 28:2","votes":13,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p44028002_01-26\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v44028002-1\">2&nbsp;</b>The native people showed us unusual kindness, for they kindled a fire and welcomed us all, because it had begun to rain and was cold.</p>\n\n</div>"},{"_id":"6164f3186451fe5325fa04dd","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"1 John 3:18","votes":12,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p id=\"p62003018_01-27\" class=\"virtual\"><b class=\"verse-num\" id=\"v62003018-1\">18&nbsp;</b>Little children, let us not love in word or talk but in deed and in truth.</p>\n</div>","modified":"2021-11-16T12:55:28.476Z"},{"_id":"6164f3186451fe5325fa04dc","topicId":"6164f3116451fe5325fa04c4","verse":"Proverbs 29:20","votes":10,"__v":0,"esv":"<div>\n<p class=\"block-indent\"><span class=\"begin-line-group\"></span>\n<span id=\"p20029020_01-28\" class=\"line\"><b class=\"verse-num inline\" id=\"v20029020-1\">20&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;Do you see a man who is hasty in his words?</span><br><span id=\"p20029020_01-28\" class=\"indent line\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;There is more hope for a fool than for him.</span><br></p><span class=\"end-line-group\"></span>\n</div>","modified":"2023-12-29T04:38:21.735Z"}]}